item.CAPTION: 重量及數量轉換及字數

CODE.item: CLEAR: G_CHARS, V_UNITP, V_KBETR, V_KBET1, SFV_STLEN, V_ZCHIP.
WRITE: WA_ITEM-KWERT CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_EXTEN.
***KPEIN位數>幣別顯示位數 =>依KPEIN位數顯示
***KPEIN位數<幣別顯示位數 =>依幣別位數顯示
ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
WRITE WA_ITEM-UNITP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
*若是要顯示twd就要固定SHOW 3位小數
* ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-UNITP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
* ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-UNITP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
***IM/EX在顯示所有值為TWD時UNIT PRICE要小數三位
* WRITE WA_ITEM-UNITP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK DECIMALS 3 TO V_UNITP.
*KPEIN位數>幣別顯示位數 =>依KPEIN位數顯示
*KPEIN位數<幣別顯示位數 =>依幣別位數顯示
ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
WRITE WA_ITEM-SCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
*若是要顯示twd就要固定SHOW 3位小數
* ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-SCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-SCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 DECIMALS 1 TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-SCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 DECIMALS 3 TO V_UNITP.
* WRITE WA_ITEM-SCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 TO V_UNITP.
*KPEIN位數>幣別顯示位數 =>依KPEIN位數顯示
*KPEIN位數<幣別顯示位數 =>依幣別位數顯示
ROUND SFV_STLEN DECIMALS SFV_STLEN TO V_UNITP.
WRITE WA_ITEM-PCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK TO V_UNITP.
*若是要顯示twd就要固定SHOW 3位小數
*WRITE WA_ITEM-PCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 DECIMALS 1 TO V_UNITP.
*WRITE WA_ITEM-PCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 DECIMALS 3 TO V_UNITP.
*WRITE WA_ITEM-PCUTP CURRENCY WA_ITEM-WAERK ROUND 1 TO V_UNITP.
